= Other Open Access projects =

These section contains links to projects which share OpenSPIM's vision that

<blockquote>
We hope that OpenSPIM in its radical openness will demonstrate
that the benefits brought to science by the Open Source approach
apply equally well to hardware.
</blockquote>

* Karl Bellve's [https://github.com/kbellve/pgFocus "pretty good focus"] project is an Open Access design for an automatic stage focusing device. It is intended to [http://valelab.ucsf.edu/~MM/MMwiki/index.php/PgFocus integrate nicely] with µManager, just like OpenSPIM.

